contentrichtext.text: '''Vian''' may refer to: * [[Vian, Iran]], a village in Hamadan Province, Iran * [[Vian, Oklahoma]], a town located in Sequoyah County, Oklahoma * [[Vian, Norway]], a town located in [[Vestvågøy]], Norway * Sir [[Philip Vian]] (1894–1968), admiral in the Royal Navy * [[Boris Vian]] (1920–1959), French writer, poet, singer, and musician * [[Dominique Vian]] (born 1944), a [[France|French]] overseas civil servant * [[Vian Smith]] (1919-1969), famous Dartmoor author from Devon who wrote extensively about horses and the Moors {{disambiguation|geo|surname}}
